summary: You're Aranea will not look like a corpse anymore. Now Aranea is super duper cute!
descriptionHtml:
04/24/2014: Hi there, back in the day, when i made this mod, there wasn't any good mods to change Aranea's looks, so i tried doing it myself, knowing nothing about moding. Although now there are plenty of good mods to change her appearance, i'll leave this mod here for all the people who likes it.
Thank you all :)



This file requires Apachiisky Hair : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
And Oriental beauty Women and Man is higly recomended : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6953

INSTALLATION: Just copy prettieraranea.esp to your data folder.
author: Ncyde
